Community Engagement Officer (Ref. 22011406-E)
Jockey Club Design Institute for Social Innovation is a unit aims at providing an innovative and human-centred platform to envision a better life in the society, connecting people with passion and nurturing doers of all ages to innovate with collective wisdom to enable impactful action. 

Duties
The appointee will be required to:
